OPINIONS on mushrooms are divided &ndash; some people love them, others not so much.But even those who aren&rsquo;t keen on fungi should probably give the Laetiporus sulphureus a try. It is also known as the chicken mushroom, or chicken of the woods.Its name gives the game away: this mushroom is said to taste like chicken!Varieties of the mushroom are found all over Europe, Africa and America.It can cause mild reactions in some people but also prevents the growth of certain bacteria.